snippet.title: TumbleSeed Teaser
snippet.description:
TumbleSeed is a rolly roguelike about a small seed with big dreams.

Roll up a procedurally generated mountain filled with holes and corrupted creatures. Reach the top and save your home! TumbleSeed features simple controls that are easy to pickup but difficult to master.  Balance the seed, grow powerful with upgrades, and meet new friends on your way to the peak.
